biosecLogger.core

Enum Logger

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Logger>
      • biosecLogger.core.Logger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Logger>

    public enum Logger
extends java.lang.Enum<Logger>
    Logger is attached to password field and using TextWatcher and SensorEvenTListener log values during login or registration.
    Author:
    Stefan Smihla
